@[to_additive (attr := elab_as_elim)
    "Dependent recursion principle for `AddLocalizations`: given elements `f a b : p (mk a b)`
for all `a b`, such that `r S (a, b) (c, d)` implies `f a b = f c d` (with the correct coercions),
